    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really great shape, super reliable, and still drives like a dream! Whether you're zipping around town or heading out on a long road trip, this beauty is ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s been well-loved and is looking for a wonderful new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
