      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, maintaining the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. A turn-key driver's car for the purist seeking high-induction acoustics and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Runs well. Clean title.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is supple and free of major blemishes, while all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule, resulting in a smooth engine note and precise handling that makes every drive a pleasure. Whether you are commuting or heading out on a weekend getaway, this car provides a reliable and stylish experience. We have kept detailed service records to ensure the next owner has full peace of mind. A solid choice for anyone seeking a high-quality pre-owned vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle exemplifies a harmonious balance between performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and showcasing commendable aesthetic and mechanical integrity, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning professional. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that has been curated to meet exacting standards of quality and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
