      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with a new owner! It runs beautifully and looks great, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend trips. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
