      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example has been meticulously maintained, with the critical double-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure precise cam timing. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. To ensure structural longevity, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this chassis is famous for. While the paint exhibits minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and chassis dynamics remain sharp and responsive. A turn-key driver's car for the purist.",
